item.title: How to make interface under a tab?(jesus at least view it!)
item.dc:creator: @guitars595 guitars595
item.description:
@guitars595 wrote:

search for setsiderbarinterface keep searching until you see like five of them in a row. In there add in setSidebarInterface(#, $$$$);
replace the # with the number of the tab you want to put it under. It starts at 0 and goes to 13, just do a little guessing to get the right tab and the $$$$ replace with your interface id.
